high_descs: Walk across the room, going past the refrigerator and the stove, stopping at the kitchen counter top between the stove and the sink, then turn to your left so that you are facing the counter.
Pick up the tea kettle on the counter, behind the marble bowl.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the sink to the far right.
Place the kettle in the sink and turn the water on for a moment, then turn the water back off.
Step back from the sink a few steps.
Place the kettle in the left, bottom cabinet, under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the rinsed, tea kettle under the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Go forward and turn left to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick the tea pot up from the counter.
Move to the right slightly and turn to face the sink.
Put the tea pot in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the tea pot up.
Back up and face the cabinets below the sink.
Put the tea pot in the cabinet and shut the doors.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tea pot in the cabinet.

high_descs: Walk straight past the fridge to the sink.
Pick up the teapot from the counter on the left of the sink.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the teapot in the sink and wash it.
Turn around and the back to the sink.
Open the cupboard under the sink and put away the teapot.
anns.task_desc: Wash the teapot and put it away under the sink.
